{"type":"message","id":"d388c19a","parentId":"a3e9b4e8","timestamp":"2026-03-03T18:03:16.729Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_af4e4028b16b4d38be245833","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Session: 2026-03-03 08:31:04 UTC\n\n- **Session Key**: agent:main:main\n- **Session ID**: 54e568d0-6198-4599-848a-b00f5689042b\n- **Source**: webchat\n\n## Conversation Summary\n\nassistant: ## 🚀 OpenClaw + Claude Code 开发团队系统实现计划\n\n这篇文章描述的是一套**双层 AI Agent 系统**，我来帮你逐步实现。\n\n---\n\n## 📋 系统架构概览\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│  编排层 (OpenClaw/Zoe)                              │\n│  - 持有业务上下文 (Obsidian/会议记录/客户数据)       │\n│  - 任务拆解 & Prompt 工程                            │\n│  - Agent 调度 (Codex/Claude Code/Gemini)            │\n│  - 监控 & 重试 & 通知 (Telegram)                    │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                          ↓\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│  执行层 (Agents)                                    │\n│  - 独立 worktree + tmux 会话                        │\n│  - 读写代码 & 运行测试                              │\n│  - 创建 PR & 响应 review                            │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🛠️ 实现步骤\n\n### 第 1 步：确认当前配置状态\n\n```bash\n# 检查 OpenClaw 配置\nopenclaw status\n\n# 检查已启用的 skills\nopenclaw skills list\n\n# 检查工具权限\nopenclaw config show tools\n```\n\n### 第 2 步：配置模型提供商\n\n根据你之前的配置，需要确保以下模型可用：\n\n| 模型 | 用途 | 提供商 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| `gpt-5.3-codex` | 后端逻辑、复杂 bug | Codex |\n| `claude-opus-4.5` | 前端、git 操作 | Claude Code |\n| `gemini-pro` | UI 设计 | Gemini |\n\n在 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` 中添加：\n\n```json\n\"models\": {\n  \"providers\": {\n    \"anthropic\": {\n      \"baseUrl\": \"https://coding.dashscope.aliyuncs.com/apps/anthropic\",\n      \"apiKey\": \"sk-sp-7eeda6dd5dbf467ba8db9454b23d0acf\",\n      \"api\": \"anthropic-completions\",\n      \"models\": [\n        {\"id\": \"kimi-k2.5\", \"name\": \"Kimi K2.5\"},\n        {\"id\": \"claude-opus-4.5\", \"name\": \"Claude Opus\"},\n        {\"id\": \"qwen3.5-plus\", \"name\": \"Qwen 3.5 Plus\"}\n      ]\n    },\n    \"openai\": {\n      \"baseUrl\": \"https://api.openai.com/v1\",\n      \"apiKey\": \"your-openai-key\",\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"models\": [\n        {\"id\": \"gpt-5.3-codex\", \"name\": \"GPT-5.3 Codex\"}\n      ]\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 第 3 步：创建目录结构\n\n```bash\n# 创建 Agent 工作区\nmkdir -p ~/openclaw-agents/{worktrees,scripts,logs,tasks}\n\n# 创建监控脚本目录\nmkdir -p ~/openclaw-agents/scripts/{monitor,review,notify}\n```\n\n### 第 4 步：创建 Agent 启动脚本\n\n`~/openclaw-agents/scripts/start-agent.sh`:\n\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\n# 启动一个 Agent 任务\n\nTASK_ID=$1\nAGENT_TYPE=$2  # codex | claude | gemini\nPROMPT_FILE=$3\nWORKTREE_NAME=$4\n\n# 创建 worktree\ngit worktree add ~/openclaw-agents/worktrees/$WORKTREE_NAME -b feat/$TASK_ID origin/main\ncd ~/openclaw-agents/worktrees/$WORKTREE_NAME\npnpm install\n\n# 启动 tmux 会话\ntmux new-session -d -s \"$AGENT_TYPE-$TASK_ID\" \\\n  -c \"~/openclaw-agents/worktrees/$WORKTREE_NAME\" \\\n  \"$HOME/.codex-agent/run-agent.sh $TASK_ID $AGENT_TYPE high\"\n\n# 记录任务\ncat >> ~/openclaw-agents/tasks/$TASK_ID.json << EOF\n{\n  \"id\": \"$TASK_ID\",\n  \"tmuxSession\": \"$AGENT_TYPE-$TASK_ID\",\n  \"agent\": \"$AGENT_TYPE\",\n  \"worktree\": \"$WORKTREE_NAME\",\n  \"branch\": \"feat/$TASK_ID\",\n  \"startedAt\": $(date +%s),\n  \"status\": \"running\"\n}\nEOF\n\necho \"Agent $TASK_ID started in tmux session $AGENT_TYPE-$TASK_ID\"\n```\n\n### 第 5 步：创建监控脚本\n\n`~/openclaw-agents/scripts/monitor/loop.sh`:\n\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\n# 改进版 Ralph Loop - 监控所有 Agent 任务\n\nTASKS_DIR=~/openclaw-agents/tasks\nLOGS_DIR=~/openclaw-agents/logs\n\nfor task_file in $TASKS_DIR/*.json; do\n  [ -f \"$task_file\" ] || continue\n  \n  TASK_ID=$(jq -r '.id' \"$task_file\")\n  TMUX_SESSION=$(jq -r '.tmuxSession' \"$task_file\")\n  STATUS=$(jq -r '.status' \"$task_file\")\n  \n  # 检查 tmux 会话是否存活\n  if ! tmux has-session -t $TMUX_SESSION 2>/dev/null; then\n    echo \"[$TASK_ID] Session dead, checking PR status...\"\n    \n    # 检查是否有 PR\n    PR_URL=$(grep -r \"Created PR\" $LOGS_DIR/$TASK_ID*.log | tail -1 | awk '{print $NF}')\n    \n    if [ -n \"$PR_URL\" ]; then\n      # 检查 CI 状态\n      CI_STATUS=$(gh pr view $PR_URL --json checkSuites --jq '.checkSuites[0].status')\n      \n      if [ \"$CI_STATUS\" = \"COMPLETED\" ]; then\n        # 通知人工 review\n        curl -X POST \"https://api.telegram.org/bot$TG_BOT_TOKEN/sendMessage\" \\\n          -d \"chat_id=$TG_CHAT_ID&text=PR $PR_URL ready for review\"\n        \n        jq '.status = \"ready_review\"' $task_file > $task_file.tmp\n        mv $task_file.tmp $task_file\n      fi\n    fi\n  fi\ndone\n```\n\n### 第 6 步：配置 Cron 监控\n\n```bash\n# 编辑 crontab\ncrontab -e\n\n# 添加每 10 分钟检查一次\n*/10 * * * * ~/openclaw-agents/scripts/monitor/loop.sh >> ~/openclaw-agents/logs/monitor.log 2>&1\n```\n\n### 第 7 步：配置自动化 Code Review\n\n`.github/workflows/auto-review.yml`:\n\n```yaml\nname: Auto Code Review\n\non:\n  pull_request:\n    types: [opened, synchronize]\n\njobs:\n  codex-review:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n      - name: Codex Review\n        uses: openai/codex-review@v1\n        with:\n          api-key: ${{ secrets.OPENAI_API_KEY }}\n          \n  claude-review:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n      - name: Claude Review\n        uses: anthropic/claude-review@v1\n        with:\n          api-key: ${{ secrets.ANTHROPIC_API_KEY }}\n          \n  ci-checks:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n      - run: pnpm install\n      - run: pnpm lint\n      - run: pnpm typecheck\n      - run: pnpm test\n      - run: pnpm test:e2e\n```\n\n### 第 8 步：配置 Telegram 通知\n\n在 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` 中添加：\n\n```json\n\"notifications\": {\n  \"telegram\": {\n    \"botToken\": \"YOUR_BOT_TOKEN\",\n    \"chatId\": \"YOUR_CHAT_ID\",\n    \"events\": [\"pr_ready\", \"agent_failed\", \"task_complete\"]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📝 OpenClaw 编排层配置\n\n在 `~/openclaw-agents/zoe-config.json` 中定义任务调度规则：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"agentSelection\": {\n    \"backend\": \"gpt-5.3-codex\",\n    \"frontend\": \"claude-opus-4.5\",\n    \"ui-design\": \"gemini-pro\",\n    \"default\": \"gpt-5.3-codex\"\n  },\n  \"retryPolicy\": {\n    \"maxRetries\": 3,\n    \"backoffSeconds\": 300\n  },\n  \"contextSources\": [\n    \"~/obsidian/notes\",\n    \"~/obsidian/meetings\",\n    \"production-db-readonly\"\n  ],\n  \"notifyOnComplete\": true,\n  \"autoMerge\": false\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 验证清单\n\n```bash\n# 1. 检查模型配置\nopenclaw status\n\n# 2. 测试 Agent 启动\n~/openclaw-agents/scripts/start-agent.sh test-task codex \"Hello World\" test-worktree\n\n# 3. 检查 tmux 会话\ntmux list-sessions\n\n# 4. 检查监控脚本\n~/openclaw-agents/scripts/monitor/loop.sh\n\n# 5. 检查 GitHub Actions\ngh workflow list\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 下一步\n\n请告诉我：\n\n1. **你当前的 OpenClaw 配置状态**（运行 `openclaw status`）\n2. **你有哪些 API 密钥**（OpenAI/Claude/Gemini）\n3. **你的代码库类型**（前端/后端/全栈）\n4. **你想优先实现哪个部分**（Agent 启动/监控/Review/通知）\n\n我会根据你的情况调整实现方案！🦞\nuser: Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-03 15:09 GMT+8] 按照这个架构，给我的代码库实现一套 Agent 集群系统。\nassistant: ## 🚀 实现 Agent 集群系统\n\n我需要先了解你的当前状态，然后逐步实现这套系统。\n\n### ⚠️ 当前限制说明\n\n我目前**没有文件读写权限**，无法直接创建文件或执行命令。但我可以：\n- ✅ 提供完整的配置文件内容\n- ✅ 提供所有脚本代码\n- ✅ 指导你逐步执行\n\n---\n\n## 📋 第一步：信息收集\n\n请回答以下问题，我会据此调整方案：\n\n### 1️⃣ OpenClaw 状态\n```bash\nopenclaw status\n```\n请粘贴输出结果。\n\n### 2️⃣ 可用模型\n```bash\nopenclaw config show models\n```\n或告诉我你有哪些 API 密钥：\n- [ ] OpenAI (Codex/GPT)\n- [ ] Anthropic (Claude)\n- [ ] Gemini\n- [ ] 其他：_______\n\n### 3️⃣ 代码库信息\n- **仓库类型：** 前端 / 后端 / 全栈 / 其他\n- **语言：** JavaScript / TypeScript / Python / 其他\n- **包管理器：** npm / pnpm / yarn / 其他\n- **托管平台：** GitHub / GitLab / 其他\n- **仓库路径：** `________________`\n\n### 4️⃣ 通知方式\n- [ ] Telegram\n- [ ] 邮件\n- [ ] 微信\n- [ ] 其他：_______\n\n---\n\n## 📁 完整实现方案\n\n以下是**完整的文件结构和内容**，你可以直接复制使用：\n\n### 目录结构\n\n```\n~/openclaw-agents/\n├── worktrees/           # Agent 工作区\n├── scripts/\n│   ├── start-agent.sh   # 启动 Agent\n│   ├── monitor/\n│   │   └── loop.sh      # 监控循环\n│   ├── review/\n│   │   └── auto-review.sh\n│   └── notify/\n│       └── telegram.sh\n├── tasks/               # 任务记录\n├── logs/                # 日志\n└── config.json          # 配置\n```\n\n---\n\n### 文件 1: `~/openclaw-agents/config.json`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"agentSelection\": {\n    \"backend\": \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\",\n    \"frontend\": \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\",\n    \"ui-design\": \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\",\n    \"default\": \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\"\n  },\n  \"retryPolicy\": {\n    \"maxRetries\": 3,\n    \"backoffSeconds\": 300\n  },\n  \"contextSources\": [\n    \"~/obsidian/notes\",\n    \"~/obsidian/meetings\"\n  ],\n  \"notifyOnComplete\": true,\n  \"autoMerge\": false,\n  \"telegram\": {\n    \"enabled\": false,\n    \"botToken\": \"\",\n    \"chatId\": \"\"\n  },\n  \"github\": {\n    \"repo\": \"\",\n    \"requireReviews\": 3\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 文件 2: `~/openclaw-agents/scripts/start-agent.sh`\n\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\n# 启动一个 Agent 任务\n# 用法: ./start-agent.sh <task_id> <agent_type> <prompt> <worktree_name>\n\nset -e\n\nTASK_ID=$1\nAGENT_TYPE=${2:-default}\nPROMPT=$3\nWORKTREE_NAME=${4:-$TASK_ID}\n\nAGENTS_ROOT=~/openclaw-agents\nWORKTREES_DIR=$AGENTS_ROOT/worktrees\nTASKS_DIR=$AGENTS_ROOT/tasks\nLOGS_DIR=$AGENTS_ROOT/logs\n\n# 创建目录\nmkdir -p \"$WORKTREES_DIR\" \"$TASKS_DIR\" \"$LOGS_DIR\"\n\n# 创建 worktree\necho \"🌳 Creating worktree: $WORKTREE_NAME\"\ngit worktree add \"$WORKTREES_DIR/$WORKTREE_NAME\" -b \"feat/$TASK_ID\" origin/main 2>/dev/null || {\n    echo \"Worktree exists, cleaning...\"\n    git worktree remove \"$WORKTREES_DIR/$WORKTREE_NAME\" 2>/dev/null || true\n    git worktree add \"$WORKTREES_DIR/$WORKTREE_NAME\" -b \"feat/$TASK_ID\" origin/main\n}\n\ncd \"$WORKTREES_DIR/$WORKTREE_NAME\"\n\n# 安装依赖\necho \"📦 Installing dependencies...\"\npnpm install --silent 2>/dev/null || npm install --silent 2>/dev/null || true\n\n# 启动 tmux 会话\nTMUX_SESSION=\"$AGENT_TYPE-$TASK_ID\"\necho \"🤖 Starting agent in tmux: $TMUX_SESSION\"\n\ntmux new-session -d -s \"$TMUX_SESSION\" \\\n    -c \"$WORKTREES_DIR/$WORKTREE_NAME\"\n\n# 发送 prompt 到会话\ntmux send-keys -t \"$TMUX_SESSION\" \"echo 'Task: $TASK_ID'\" Enter\ntmux send-keys -t \"$TMUX_SESSION\" \"echo 'Prompt: $PROMPT'\" Enter\ntmux send-keys -t \"$TMUX_SESSION\" \"# Agent ready for instructions\" Enter\n\n# 记录任务\ncat > \"$TASKS_DIR/$TASK_ID.json\" << EOF\n{\n  \"id\": \"$TASK_ID\",\n  \"tmuxSession\": \"$TMUX_SESSION\",\n  \"agent\": \"$AGENT_TYPE\",\n  \"worktree\": \"$WORKTREE_NAME\",\n  \"branch\": \"feat/$TASK_ID\",\n  \"startedAt\": $(date +%s),\n  \"status\": \"running\",\n  \"prompt\": \"$PROMPT\"\n}\nEOF\n\necho \"✅ Agent $TASK_ID started in tmux session $TMUX_SESSION\"\necho \"   Attach with: tmux attach -t $TMUX_SESSION\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### 文件 3: `~/openclaw-agents/scripts/monitor/loop.sh`\n\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\n# 改进版 Ralph Loop - 监控所有 Agent 任务\n\nAGENTS_ROOT=~/openclaw-agents\nTASKS_DIR=$AGENTS_ROOT/tasks\nLOGS_DIR=$AGENTS_ROOT/logs\nCONFIG_FILE=$AGENTS_ROOT/config.json\n\n# 读取配置\nTELEGRAM_ENABLED=$(jq -r '.telegram.enabled' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"false\")\nTELEGRAM_TOKEN=$(jq -r '.telegram.botToken' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"\")\nTELEGRAM_CHAT_ID=$(jq -r '.telegram.chatId' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"\")\n\nnotify_telegram() {\n    local message=\"$1\"\n    if [ \"$TELEGRAM_ENABLED\" = \"true\" ] && [ -n \"$TELEGRAM_TOKEN\" ]; then\n        curl -s -X POST \"https://api.telegram.org/bot$TELEGRAM_TOKEN/sendMessage\" \\\n            -d \"chat_id=$TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID&text=$message\" > /dev/null\n    fi\n    echo \"[NOTIFY] $message\"\n}\n\nfor task_file in \"$TASKS_DIR\"/*.json; do\n    [ -f \"$task_file\" ] || continue\n    \n    TASK_ID=$(jq -r '.id' \"$task_file\" 2>/dev/null)\n    TMUX_SESSION=$(jq -r '.tmuxSession' \"$task_file\" 2>/dev/null)\n    STATUS=$(jq -r '.status' \"$task_file\" 2>/dev/null)\n    BRANCH=$(jq -r '.branch' \"$task_file\" 2>/dev/null)\n    \n    [ -z \"$TASK_ID\" ] && continue\n    \n    # 检查 tmux 会话是否存活\n    if ! tmux has-session -t \"$TMUX_SESSION\" 2>/dev/null; then\n        echo \"[$TASK_ID] Session ended, checking results...\"\n        \n        # 检查是否有 PR 创建\n        PR_LOG=$(grep -r \"Created PR\\|Pull request\" \"$LOGS_DIR/$TASK_ID\"*.log 2>/dev/null | tail -1 || echo \"\")\n        \n        if [ -n \"$PR_LOG\" ]; then\n            PR_URL=$(echo \"$PR_LOG\" | grep -oE 'https://github.com[^ ]+')\n            \n            if [ -n \"$PR_URL\" ]; then\n                # 检查 CI 状态 (需要 gh CLI)\n                if command -v gh &> /dev/null; then\n                    CI_STATUS=$(gh pr view \"$PR_URL\" --json checkSuites --jq '.checkSuites[0].status' 2>/dev/null || echo \"UNKNOWN\")\n                    \n                    if [ \"$CI_STATUS\" = \"COMPLETED\" ] || [ \"$CI_STATUS\" = \"UNKNOWN\" ]; then\n                        notify_telegram \"🎉 PR #$TASK_ID ready for review: $PR_URL\"\n                        \n                        # 更新任务状态\n                        jq '.status = \"ready_review\"' \"$task_file\" > \"$task_file.tmp\"\n                        mv \"$task_file.tmp\" \"$task_file\"\n                    fi\n                else\n                    notify_telegram \"🎉 PR #$TASK_ID ready for review: $PR_URL\"\n                    jq '.status = \"ready_review\"' \"$task_file\" > \"$task_file.tmp\"\n                    mv \"$task_file.tmp\" \"$task_file\"\n                fi\n            fi\n        else\n            # 任务失败，检查重试\n            RETRY_COUNT=$(jq -r '.retryCount // 0' \"$task_file\")\n            MAX_RETRIES=$(jq -r '.retryPolicy.maxRetries' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"3\")\n            \n            if [ \"$RETRY_COUNT\" -lt \"$MAX_RETRIES\" ]; then\n                echo \"[$TASK_ID] Retrying... ($RETRY_COUNT/$MAX_RETRIES)\"\n                jq '.retryCount = (.retryCount // 0) + 1 | .status = \"retrying\"' \"$task_file\" > \"$task_file.tmp\"\n                mv \"$task_file.tmp\" \"$task_file\"\n                # 这里可以添加自动重试逻辑\n            else\n                notify_telegram \"❌ Task #$TASK_ID failed after $MAX_RETRIES retries\"\n                jq '.status = \"failed\"' \"$task_file\" > \"$task_file.tmp\"\n                mv \"$task_file.tmp\" \"$task_file\"\n            fi\n        fi\n    fi\ndone\n\necho \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] Monitor loop completed\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### 文件 4: `~/openclaw-agents/scripts/review/auto-review.sh`\n\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\n# 自动化 Code Review 脚本\n\nPR_URL=$1\nREVIEWER=${2:-all}  # codex | claude | gemini | all\n\nif [ -z \"$PR_URL\" ]; then\n    echo \"Usage: ./auto-review.sh <pr_url> [reviewer]\"\n    exit 1\nfi\n\n# 提取 repo 信息\nREPO=$(echo \"$PR_URL\" | sed -E 's|https://github.com/([^/]+/[^/]+)/pull.*|\\1|')\nPR_NUMBER=$(echo \"$PR_URL\" | sed -E 's|.*/pull/([0-9]+)|\\1|')\n\necho \"🔍 Reviewing PR #$PR_NUMBER in $REPO\"\n\n# 检出 PR\ngit fetch origin pull/$PR_NUMBER/head:pr-$PR_NUMBER\ngit checkout pr-$PR_NUMBER\n\n# 运行本地检查\necho \"📋 Running lint...\"\npnpm lint 2>/dev/null || npm run lint 2>/dev/null || echo \"No lint script\"\n\necho \"📋 Running typecheck...\"\npnpm typecheck 2>/dev/null || npm run typecheck 2>/dev/null || echo \"No typecheck script\"\n\necho \"📋 Running tests...\"\npnpm test 2>/dev/null || npm test 2>/dev/null || echo \"No test script\"\n\n# AI Review (需要配置 API)\nif [ \"$REVIEWER\" = \"codex\" ] || [ \"$REVIEWER\" = \"all\" ]; then\n    echo \"🤖 Codex review...\"\n    # 调用 Codex API 进行 review\nfi\n\nif [ \"$REVIEWER\" = \"claude\" ] || [ \"$REVIEWER\" = \"all\" ]; then\n    echo \"🤖 Claude review...\"\n    # 调用 Claude API 进行 review\nfi\n\n# 提交 review 结果\n# gh pr review $PR_NUMBER --comment \"Auto-review completed\"\n\necho \"✅ Review completed for PR #$PR_NUMBER\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### 文件 5: `~/openclaw-agents/scripts/notify/telegram.sh`\n\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\n# Telegram 通知脚本\n\nTOKEN=$1\nCHAT_ID=$2\nMESSAGE=$3\n\nif [ -z \"$TOKEN\" ] || [ -z \"$CHAT_ID\" ] || [ -z \"$MESSAGE\" ]; then\n    echo \"Usage: ./telegram.sh <token> <chat_id> <message>\"\n    exit 1\nfi\n\ncurl -s -X POST \"https://api.telegram.org/bot$TOKEN/sendMessage\" \\\n    -d \"chat_id=$CHAT_ID&text=$MESSAGE&parse_mode=Markdown\"\n\necho \"Notification sent\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### 文件 6: `~/.github/workflows/auto-review.yml`\n\n```yaml\nname: Auto Code Review\n\non:\n  pull_request:\n    types: [opened, synchronize, reopened]\n\njobs:\n  ci-checks:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n      \n      - name: Setup Node.js\n        uses: actions/setup-node@v4\n        with:\n          node-version: '20'\n          \n      - name: Install dependencies\n        run: pnpm install --frozen-lockfile || npm ci\n        \n      - name: Lint\n        run: pnpm lint || npm run lint\n        \n      - name: Type Check\n        run: pnpm typecheck || npm run typecheck\n        \n      - name: Test\n        run: pnpm test || npm test\n        \n      - name: E2E Test\n        run: pnpm test:e2e || npm run test:e2e\n        continue-on-error: true\n\n  codex-review:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    needs: ci-checks\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n      \n      - name: Codex Review\n        uses: actions/github-script@v7\n        with:\n          script: |\n            // 调用 Codex API 进行 review\n            console.log('Codex review in progress...')\n\n  claude-review:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    needs: ci-checks\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n      \n      - name: Claude Review\n        uses: actions/github-script@v7\n        with:\n          script: |\n            // 调用 Claude API 进行 review\n            console.log('Claude review in progress...')\n```\n\n---\n\n### 文件 7: `~/openclaw-agents/zoe-config.json` (编排层配置)\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"Zoe\",\n  \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n  \"agentSelection\": {\n    \"rules\": [\n      {\n        \"pattern\": \"backend|api|database|server\",\n        \"agent\": \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"pattern\": \"frontend|ui|component|style\",\n        \"agent\": \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"pattern\": \"design|mockup|prototype\",\n        \"agent\": \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"pattern\": \".*\",\n        \"agent\": \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\"\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  \"contextManagement\": {\n    \"obsidianPath\": \"~/obsidian\",\n    \"meetingNotesPath\": \"~/obsidian/meetings\",\n    \"customerDataPath\": \"~/obsidian/customers\",\n    \"autoSync\": true\n  },\n  \"taskPipeline\": {\n    \"steps\": [\n      \"understand\",\n      \"plan\",\n      \"execute\",\n      \"review\",\n      \"submit\"\n    ],\n    \"autoRetry\": true,\n    \"maxRetries\": 3\n  },\n  \"notifications\": {\n    \"onTaskStart\": false,\n    \"onTaskComplete\": true,\n    \"onTaskFailed\": true,\n    \"onPRReady\": true,\n    \"channels\": [\"telegram\"]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 设置步骤\n\n### 步骤 1: 创建目录结构\n\n```bash\nmkdir -p ~/openclaw-agents/{worktrees,scripts/{monitor,review,notify},tasks,logs}\n```\n\n### 步骤 2: 创建所有文件\n\n将上面的文件内容分别保存到对应路径。\n\n### 步骤 3: 设置执行权限\n\n```bash\nchmod +x ~/openclaw-agents/scripts/*.sh\nchmod +x ~/openclaw-agents/scripts/*/*.sh\n```\n\n### 步骤 4: 配置 Cron 监控\n\n```bash\ncrontab -e\n\n# 添加以下行（每 10 分钟检查一次）\n*/10 * * * * ~/openclaw-agents/scripts/monitor/loop.sh >> ~/openclaw-agents/logs/monitor.log 2>&1\n```\n\n### 步骤 5: 配置 Telegram 通知（可选）\n\n1. 联系 @BotFather 创建 bot，获取 token\n2. 获取你的 chat ID（联系 @userinfobot）\n3. 更新 `~/openclaw-agents/config.json` 中的 telegram 配置\n\n### 步骤 6: 测试系统\n\n```bash\n# 测试启动 Agent\n~/openclaw-agents/scripts/start-agent.sh test-task default \"Hello World\" test-worktree\n\n# 检查 tmux 会话\ntmux list-sessions\n\n# 测试监控脚本\n~/openclaw-agents/scripts/monitor/loop.sh\n```\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 验证清单\n\n```bash\n# 1. 检查目录结构\nls -la ~/openclaw-agents/\n\n# 2. 检查脚本权限\nls -la ~/openclaw-agents/scripts/\n\n# 3. 测试 Agent 启动\n~/openclaw-agents/scripts/start-agent.sh demo-task default \"Test\" demo\n\n# 4. 检查 tmux\ntmux list-sessions\n\n# 5. 检查任务记录\ncat ~/openclaw-agents/tasks/demo-task.json\n\n# 6. 测试监控\n~/openclaw-agents/scripts/monitor/loop.sh\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 现在请执行\n\n```bash\n# 1. 创建目录\nmkdir -p ~/openclaw-agents/{worktrees,scripts/{monitor,review,notify},tasks,logs}\n\n# 2. 告诉我你的代码库信息（见上面的问题）\n\n# 3. 我会根据你的情况调整配置\n```\n\n请告诉我：\n1. **你的代码库路径和类型**\n2. **你有哪些 API 密钥**\n3. **是否需要 Telegram 通知**\n\n我会帮你完成剩余的配置！🦞\nuser: Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-03 15:12 GMT+8] 按你的路径就行，我有本地的claudecode 还有大模型的api 然后只需要邮件通知就行\nassistant: ## 🚀 好的！按我的方案实现，调整为邮件通知\n\n---\n\n## 📁 完整实现（邮件通知版）\n\n### 步骤 1: 创建目录结构\n\n```bash\nmkdir -p ~/openclaw-agents/{worktrees,scripts/{monitor,review,notify},tasks,logs}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 步骤 2: 创建配置文件 `~/openclaw-agents/config.json`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"agentSelection\": {\n    \"backend\": \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\",\n    \"frontend\": \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\",\n    \"ui-design\": \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\",\n    \"default\": \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\"\n  },\n  \"retryPolicy\": {\n    \"maxRetries\": 3,\n    \"backoffSeconds\": 300\n  },\n  \"contextSources\": [\n    \"~/obsidian/notes\",\n    \"~/obsidian/meetings\"\n  ],\n  \"notifyOnComplete\": true,\n  \"autoMerge\": false,\n  \"email\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"smtpServer\": \"smtp.gmail.com\",\n    \"smtpPort\": 587,\n    \"username\": \"your-email@gmail.com\",\n    \"password\": \"your-app-password\",\n    \"from\": \"your-email@gmail.com\",\n    \"to\": \"your-email@gmail.com\"\n  },\n  \"github\": {\n    \"repo\": \"\",\n    \"requireReviews\": 3\n  },\n  \"claudeCode\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"path\": \"~/.codex-agent/run-agent.sh\",\n    \"model\": \"claude-opus-4.5\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 步骤 3: 创建启动脚本 `~/openclaw-agents/scripts/start-agent.sh`\n\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\n# 启动一个 Agent 任务\n# 用法: ./start-agent.sh <task_id> <agent_type> <prompt> <worktree_name>\n\nset -e\n\nTASK_ID=$1\nAGENT_TYPE=${2:-default}\nPROMPT=$3\nWORKTREE_NAME=${4:-$TASK_ID}\n\nAGENTS_ROOT=~/openclaw-agents\nWORKTREES_DIR=$AGENTS_ROOT/worktrees\nTASKS_DIR=$AGENTS_ROOT/tasks\nLOGS_DIR=$AGENTS_ROOT/logs\nCONFIG_FILE=$AGENTS_ROOT/config.json\n\n# 创建目录\nmkdir -p \"$WORKTREES_DIR\" \"$TASKS_DIR\" \"$LOGS_DIR\"\n\n# 读取 Claude Code 配置\nCLAUDE_CODE_PATH=$(jq -r '.claudeCode.path' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"$HOME/.codex-agent/run-agent.sh\")\nCLAUDE_MODEL=$(jq -r '.claudeCode.model' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"claude-opus-4.5\")\n\n# 创建 worktree\necho \"🌳 Creating worktree: $WORKTREE_NAME\"\ncd ~/your-repo-path  # 替换为你的代码库路径\ngit worktree add \"$WORKTREES_DIR/$WORKTREE_NAME\" -b \"feat/$TASK_ID\" origin/main 2>/dev/null || {\n    echo \"Worktree exists, cleaning...\"\n    git worktree remove \"$WORKTREES_DIR/$WORKTREE_NAME\" 2>/dev/null || true\n    git worktree add \"$WORKTREES_DIR/$WORKTREE_NAME\" -b \"feat/$TASK_ID\" origin/main\n}\n\ncd \"$WORKTREES_DIR/$WORKTREE_NAME\"\n\n# 安装依赖\necho \"📦 Installing dependencies...\"\npnpm install --silent 2>/dev/null || npm install --silent 2>/dev/null || true\n\n# 启动 tmux 会话\nTMUX_SESSION=\"$AGENT_TYPE-$TASK_ID\"\nLOG_FILE=\"$LOGS_DIR/$TASK_ID.log\"\necho \"🤖 Starting agent in tmux: $TMUX_SESSION\"\n\ntmux new-session -d -s \"$TMUX_SESSION\" \\\n    -c \"$WORKTREES_DIR/$WORKTREE_NAME\"\n\n# 发送指令到会话（使用 Claude Code）\ntmux send-keys -t \"$TMUX_SESSION\" \"echo '=== Task: $TASK_ID ==='\" Enter\ntmux send-keys -t \"$TMUX_SESSION\" \"echo 'Started at: $(date)'\" Enter\ntmux send-keys -t \"$TMUX_SESSION\" \"echo 'Prompt: $PROMPT'\" Enter\ntmux send-keys -t \"$TMUX_SESSION\" \"\" Enter\ntmux send-keys -t \"$TMUX_SESSION\" \"# Running Claude Code...\" Enter\ntmux send-keys -t \"$TMUX_SESSION\" \"$CLAUDE_CODE_PATH --prompt \\\"$PROMPT\\\" --model $CLAUDE_MODEL 2>&1 | tee $LOG_FILE\" Enter\n\n# 记录任务\ncat > \"$TASKS_DIR/$TASK_ID.json\" << EOF\n{\n  \"id\": \"$TASK_ID\",\n  \"tmuxSession\": \"$TMUX_SESSION\",\n  \"agent\": \"$AGENT_TYPE\",\n  \"worktree\": \"$WORKTREE_NAME\",\n  \"branch\": \"feat/$TASK_ID\",\n  \"startedAt\": $(date +%s),\n  \"status\": \"running\",\n  \"prompt\": \"$PROMPT\",\n  \"retryCount\": 0\n}\nEOF\n\necho \"✅ Agent $TASK_ID started in tmux session $TMUX_SESSION\"\necho \"   Attach with: tmux attach -t $TMUX_SESSION\"\necho \"   Logs: $LOG_FILE\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### 步骤 4: 创建监控脚本 `~/openclaw-agents/scripts/monitor/loop.sh`\n\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\n# 改进版 Ralph Loop - 监控所有 Agent 任务\n\nAGENTS_ROOT=~/openclaw-agents\nTASKS_DIR=$AGENTS_ROOT/tasks\nLOGS_DIR=$AGENTS_ROOT/logs\nCONFIG_FILE=$AGENTS_ROOT/config.json\n\n# 读取邮件配置\nEMAIL_ENABLED=$(jq -r '.email.enabled' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"false\")\nSMTP_SERVER=$(jq -r '.email.smtpServer' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"smtp.gmail.com\")\nSMTP_PORT=$(jq -r '.email.smtpPort' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"587\")\nEMAIL_USER=$(jq -r '.email.username' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"\")\nEMAIL_PASS=$(jq -r '.email.password' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"\")\nEMAIL_FROM=$(jq -r '.email.from' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"\")\nEMAIL_TO=$(jq -r '.email.to' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"\")\n\n# 发送邮件函数\nsend_email() {\n    local subject=\"$1\"\n    local body=\"$2\"\n    \n    if [ \"$EMAIL_ENABLED\" != \"true\" ] || [ -z \"$EMAIL_USER\" ]; then\n        echo \"[EMAIL SKIP] $subject\"\n        return\n    fi\n    \n    # 使用 mail 命令或 sendmail\n    if command -v mail &> /dev/null; then\n        echo \"$body\" | mail -s \"$subject\" -r \"$EMAIL_FROM\" -S smtp=\"$SMTP_SERVER:$SMTP_PORT\" \\\n            -S smtp-auth=login -S smtp-auth-user=\"$EMAIL_USER\" -S smtp-auth-password=\"$EMAIL_PASS\" \\\n            \"$EMAIL_TO\"\n    elif command -v sendmail &> /dev/null; then\n        {\n            echo \"From: $EMAIL_FROM\"\n            echo \"To: $EMAIL_TO\"\n            echo \"Subject: $subject\"\n            echo \"\"\n            echo \"$body\"\n        } | sendmail -t\n    else\n        # 使用 Python 发送\n        python3 << PYEOF\nimport smtplib\nfrom email.mime.text import MIMEText\n\nmsg = MIMEText('''$body''')\nmsg['Subject'] = '$subject'\nmsg['From'] = '$EMAIL_FROM'\nmsg['To'] = '$EMAIL_TO'\n\ntry:\n    server = smtplib.SMTP('$SMTP_SERVER', $SMTP_PORT)\n    server.starttls()\n    server.login('$EMAIL_USER', '$EMAIL_PASS')\n    server.send_message(msg)\n    server.quit()\n    print(\"Email sent: $subject\")\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"Email failed: {e}\")\nPYEOF\n    fi\n    \n    echo \"[EMAIL SENT] $subject\"\n}\n\n# 主监控循环\nfor task_file in \"$TASKS_DIR\"/*.json; do\n    [ -f \"$task_file\" ] || continue\n    \n    TASK_ID=$(jq -r '.id' \"$task_file\" 2>/dev/null)\n    TMUX_SESSION=$(jq -r '.tmuxSession' \"$task_file\" 2>/dev/null)\n    STATUS=$(jq -r '.status' \"$task_file\" 2>/dev/null)\n    BRANCH=$(jq -r '.branch' \"$task_file\" 2>/dev/null)\n    PROMPT=$(jq -r '.prompt' \"$task_file\" 2>/dev/null)\n    \n    [ -z \"$TASK_ID\" ] && continue\n    \n    echo \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] Checking task: $TASK_ID (status: $STATUS)\"\n    \n    # 检查 tmux 会话是否存活\n    if ! tmux has-session -t \"$TMUX_SESSION\" 2>/dev/null; then\n        echo \"[$TASK_ID] Session ended, checking results...\"\n        \n        LOG_FILE=\"$LOGS_DIR/$TASK_ID.log\"\n        \n        # 检查是否有 PR 创建\n        if [ -f \"$LOG_FILE\" ]; then\n            PR_LOG=$(grep -i \"Created PR\\|Pull request\\|github.com.*/pull\" \"$LOG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null | tail -1 || echo \"\")\n        else\n            PR_LOG=\"\"\n        fi\n        \n        if [ -n \"$PR_LOG\" ]; then\n            PR_URL=$(echo \"$PR_LOG\" | grep -oE 'https://github.com[^ >]+' | head -1)\n            \n            if [ -n \"$PR_URL\" ]; then\n                # 检查 CI 状态 (需要 gh CLI)\n                if command -v gh &> /dev/null && [ -n \"$PR_URL\" ]; then\n                    CI_STATUS=$(gh pr view \"$PR_URL\" --json checkSuites --jq '.checkSuites[0].status' 2>/dev/null || echo \"UNKNOWN\")\n                    \n                    if [ \"$CI_STATUS\" = \"COMPLETED\" ] || [ \"$CI_STATUS\" = \"UNKNOWN\" ]; then\n                        send_email \"🎉 PR Ready: $TASK_ID\" \"PR #$TASK_ID is ready for review.\\n\\nURL: $PR_URL\\nTask: $PROMPT\"\n                        \n                        jq '.status = \"ready_review\" | .completedAt = '\"$(date +%s)\"'' \"$task_file\" > \"$task_file.tmp\"\n                        mv \"$task_file.tmp\" \"$task_file\"\n                    fi\n                else\n                    send_email \"🎉 PR Ready: $TASK_ID\" \"PR #$TASK_ID is ready for review.\\n\\nURL: $PR_URL\\nTask: $PROMPT\"\n                    \n                    jq '.status = \"ready_review\" | .completedAt = '\"$(date +%s)\"'' \"$task_file\" > \"$task_file.tmp\"\n                    mv \"$task_file.tmp\" \"$task_file\"\n                fi\n            else\n                # 有日志但没有 PR，可能是失败了\n                send_email \"⚠️ Task Completed: $TASK_ID\" \"Task #$TASK_ID completed but no PR created.\\n\\nPrompt: $PROMPT\\nCheck logs: $LOG_FILE\"\n                jq '.status = \"completed_no_pr\" | .completedAt = '\"$(date +%s)\"'' \"$task_file\" > \"$task_file.tmp\"\n                mv \"$task_file.tmp\" \"$task_file\"\n            fi\n        else\n            # 任务失败，检查重试\n            RETRY_COUNT=$(jq -r '.retryCount // 0' \"$task_file\")\n            MAX_RETRIES=$(jq -r '.retryPolicy.maxRetries' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"3\")\n            \n            if [ \"$RETRY_COUNT\" -lt \"$MAX_RETRIES\" ]; then\n                echo \"[$TASK_ID] Retrying... ($RETRY_COUNT/$MAX_RETRIES)\"\n                send_email \"🔄 Retrying: $TASK_ID\" \"Task #$TASK_ID failed, retrying ($RETRY_COUNT/$MAX_RETRIES).\\n\\nPrompt: $PROMPT\"\n                \n                jq '.retryCount = (.retryCount // 0) + 1 | .status = \"retrying\"' \"$task_file\" > \"$task_file.tmp\"\n                mv \"$task_file.tmp\" \"$task_file\"\n                \n                # 重新启动 Agent\n                WORKTREE=$(jq -r '.worktree' \"$task_file\")\n                cd ~/openclaw-agents/scripts\n                ./start-agent.sh \"$TASK_ID\" \"default\" \"$PROMPT\" \"$WORKTREE\"\n            else\n                send_email \"❌ Task Failed: $TASK_ID\" \"Task #$TASK_ID failed after $MAX_RETRIES retries.\\n\\nPrompt: $PROMPT\\nPlease check manually.\"\n                jq '.status = \"failed\" | .failedAt = '\"$(date +%s)\"'' \"$task_file\" > \"$task_file.tmp\"\n                mv \"$task_file.tmp\" \"$task_file\"\n            fi\n        fi\n    fi\ndone\n\necho \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] Monitor loop completed\"\n```\n\n---\n\n### 步骤 5: 创建邮件通知脚本 `~/openclaw-agents/scripts/notify/email.sh`\n\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\n# 邮件通知脚本\n# 用法: ./email.sh <subject> <body>\n\nSUBJECT=$1\nBODY=$2\n\nCONFIG_FILE=~/openclaw-agents/config.json\n\nEMAIL_ENABLED=$(jq -r '.email.enabled' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"false\")\nSMTP_SERVER=$(jq -r '.email.smtpServer' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"smtp.gmail.com\")\nSMTP_PORT=$(jq -r '.email.smtpPort' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"587\")\nEMAIL_USER=$(jq -r '.email.username' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"\")\nEMAIL_PASS=$(jq -r '.email.password' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"\")\nEMAIL_FROM=$(jq -r '.email.from' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"\")\nEMAIL_TO=$(jq -r '.email.to' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"\")\n\nif [ \"$EMAIL_ENABLED\" != \"true\" ] || [ -z \"$EMAIL_USER\" ]; then\n    echo \"Email not configured, skipping notification\"\n    exit 0\nfi\n\n# 使用 Python 发送邮件\npython3 << PYEOF\nimport smtplib\nfrom email.mime.text import MIMEText\n\nmsg = MIMEText('''$BODY''')\nmsg['Subject'] = '$SUBJECT'\nmsg['From'] = '$EMAIL_FROM'\nmsg['To'] = '$EMAIL_TO'\n\ntry:\n    server = smtplib.SMTP('$SMTP_SERVER', $SMTP_PORT)\n    server.starttls()\n    server.login('$EMAIL_USER', '$EMAIL_PASS')\n    server.send_message(msg)\n    server.quit()\n    print(\"✅ Email sent: $SUBJECT\")\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"❌ Email failed: {e}\")\n    exit(1)\nPYEOF\n```\n\n---\n\n### 步骤 6: 创建 GitHub Actions 工作流 `.github/workflows/auto-review.yml`\n\n```yaml\nname: Auto Code Review\n\non:\n  pull_request:\n    types: [opened, synchronize, reopened]\n\njobs:\n  ci-checks:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n      \n      - name: Setup Node.js\n        uses: actions/setup-node@v4\n        with:\n          node-version: '20'\n          \n      - name: Install dependencies\n        run: pnpm install --frozen-lockfile || npm ci\n        \n      - name: Lint\n        run: pnpm lint || npm run lint\n        continue-on-error: true\n        \n      - name: Type Check\n        run: pnpm typecheck || npm run typecheck\n        continue-on-error: true\n        \n      - name: Test\n        run: pnpm test || npm test\n        continue-on-error: true\n\n  notify-complete:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    needs: ci-checks\n    if: always()\n    steps:\n      - name: Notify PR Status\n        uses: actions/github-script@v7\n        with:\n          script: |\n            const status = '${{ needs.ci-checks.result }}';\n            const prNumber = context.payload.pull_request.number;\n            console.log(`PR #${prNumber} CI status: ${status}`);\n```\n\n---\n\n### 步骤 7: 设置 Cron 监控\n\n```bash\n# 编辑 crontab\ncrontab -e\n\n# 添加以下行（每 10 分钟检查一次）\n*/10 * * * * ~/openclaw-agents/scripts/monitor/loop.sh >> ~/openclaw-agents/logs/monitor.log 2>&1\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 完整设置命令\n\n```bash\n# ===== 1. 创建目录 =====\nmkdir -p ~/openclaw-agents/{worktrees,scripts/{monitor,review,notify},tasks,logs}\n\n# ===== 2. 创建配置文件 =====\ncat > ~/openclaw-agents/config.json << 'EOF'\n{\n  \"agentSelection\": {\n    \"backend\": \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\",\n    \"frontend\": \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\",\n    \"ui-design\": \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\",\n    \"default\": \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\"\n  },\n  \"retryPolicy\": {\n    \"maxRetries\": 3,\n    \"backoffSeconds\": 300\n  },\n  \"email\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"smtpServer\": \"smtp.gmail.com\",\n    \"smtpPort\": 587,\n    \"username\": \"YOUR_EMAIL@gmail.com\",\n    \"password\": \"YOUR_APP_PASSWORD\",\n    \"from\": \"YOUR_EMAIL@gmail.com\",\n    \"to\": \"YOUR_EMAIL@gmail.com\"\n  },\n  \"claudeCode\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"path\": \"~/.codex-agent/run-agent.sh\",\n    \"model\": \"claude-opus-4.5\"\n  }\n}\nEOF\n\n# ===== 3. 创建启动脚本 =====\n# (复制上面的 start-agent.sh 内容)\n\n# ===== 4. 创建监控脚本 =====\n# (复制上面的 loop.sh 内容)\n\n# ===== 5. 创建邮件脚本 =====\n# (复制上面的 email.sh 内容)\n\n# ===== 6. 设置执行权限 =====\nchmod +x ~/openclaw-agents/scripts/*.sh\nchmod +x ~/openclaw-agents/scripts/*/*.sh\n\n# ===== 7. 配置 Cron =====\n(crontab -l 2>/dev/null; echo \"*/10 * * * * ~/openclaw-agents/scripts/monitor/loop.sh >> ~/openclaw-agents/logs/monitor.log 2>&1\") | crontab -\n\n# ===== 8. 验证 =====\ncrontab -l\nls -la ~/openclaw-agents/\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📧 邮件配置说明\n\n### Gmail 用户：\n1. 启用两步验证\n2. 生成应用专用密码：https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords\n3. 在 `config.json` 中填写：\n   - `username`: 你的 Gmail 地址\n   - `password`: 应用专用密码（不是登录密码）\n\n### 其他邮箱：\n| 邮箱 | SMTP Server | Port |\n|------|-------------|------|\n| Gmail | smtp.gmail.com | 587 |\n| Outlook | smtp.office365.com | 587 |\n| QQ 邮箱 | smtp.qq.com | 587 |\n| 163 邮箱 | smtp.163.com | 587 |\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 验证清单\n\n```bash\n# 1. 检查目录结构\nls -la ~/openclaw-agents/\n\n# 2. 检查配置文件\ncat ~/openclaw-agents/config.json\n\n# 3. 测试邮件发送\n~/openclaw-agents/scripts/notify/email.sh \"Test Subject\" \"Test Body\"\n\n# 4. 测试 Agent 启动（替换为你的代码库路径）\ncd ~/openclaw-agents/scripts\n./start-agent.sh test-task default \"Hello World\" test-worktree\n\n# 5. 检查 tmux\ntmux list-sessions\n\n# 6. 检查任务记录\ncat ~/openclaw-agents/tasks/test-task.json\n\n# 7. 测试监控\n~/openclaw-agents/scripts/monitor/loop.sh\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 下一步\n\n请执行以下命令开始：\n\n```bash\n# 1. 创建目录\nmkdir -p ~/openclaw-agents/{worktrees,scripts/{monitor,review,notify},tasks,logs}\n\n# 2. 告诉我你的代码库路径（替换 ~/your-repo-path）\n# 3. 告诉我你的邮箱地址（用于配置邮件通知）\n```\n\n完成后告诉我，我会帮你验证配置！🦞\nuser: Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-03 15:27 GMT+8] /Users/lihzz/openclawCode 793323821@qq.com\nassistant: ## 🚀 完美！开始创建完整配置\n\n你的信息：\n- **代码库路径：** `/Users/lihzz/openclawCode`\n- **邮箱：** `793323821@qq.com`\n\n---\n\n## 📧 QQ 邮箱配置说明\n\nQQ 邮箱需要使用**授权码**（不是登录密码）：\n\n1. 登录 QQ 邮箱网页版\n2. 设置 → 账户 → 开启 SMTP 服务\n3. 生成授权码\n4. 将授权码填入配置文件\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 执行以下命令创建完整系统\n\n### 步骤 1: 创建目录结构\n\n```bash\nmkdir -p ~/openclaw-agents/{worktrees,scripts/{monitor,review,notify},tasks,logs}\n```\n\n### 步骤 2: 创建配置文件\n\n```bash\ncat > ~/openclaw-agents/config.json << 'EOF'\n{\n  \"agentSelection\": {\n    \"backend\": \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\",\n    \"frontend\": \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\",\n    \"ui-design\": \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\",\n    \"default\": \"anthropic/kimi-k2.5\"\n  },\n  \"retryPolicy\": {\n    \"maxRetries\": 3,\n    \"backoffSeconds\": 300\n  },\n  \"email\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"smtpServer\": \"smtp.qq.com\",\n    \"smtpPort\": 587,\n    \"username\": \"793323821@qq.com\",\n    \"password\": \"YOUR_QQ_AUTH_CODE\",\n    \"from\": \"793323821@qq.com\",\n    \"to\": \"793323821@qq.com\"\n  },\n  \"claudeCode\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"path\": \"~/.codex-agent/run-agent.sh\",\n    \"model\": \"claude-opus-4.5\"\n  },\n  \"github\": {\n    \"repo\": \"\",\n    \"requireReviews\": 3\n  }\n}\nEOF\n```\n\n### 步骤 3: 创建启动脚本\n\n```bash\ncat > ~/openclaw-agents/scripts/start-agent.sh << 'SCRIPT'\n#!/bin/bash\n# 启动一个 Agent 任务\n# 用法: ./start-agent.sh <task_id> <agent_type> <prompt> <worktree_name>\n\nset -e\n\nTASK_ID=$1\nAGENT_TYPE=${2:-default}\nPROMPT=$3\nWORKTREE_NAME=${4:-$TASK_ID}\n\nAGENTS_ROOT=~/openclaw-agents\nWORKTREES_DIR=$AGENTS_ROOT/worktrees\nTASKS_DIR=$AGENTS_ROOT/tasks\nLOGS_DIR=$AGENTS_ROOT/logs\nCONFIG_FILE=$AGENTS_ROOT/config.json\nREPO_PATH=~/openclawCode\n\n# 读取 Claude Code 配置\nCLAUDE_CODE_PATH=$(jq -r '.claudeCode.path' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"$HOME/.codex-agent/run-agent.sh\")\nCLAUDE_MODEL=$(jq -r '.claudeCode.model' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"claude-opus-4.5\")\n\n# 创建目录\nmkdir -p \"$WORKTREES_DIR\" \"$TASKS_DIR\" \"$LOGS_DIR\"\n\n# 创建 worktree\necho \"🌳 Creating worktree: $WORKTREE_NAME\"\ncd \"$REPO_PATH\"\ngit worktree add \"$WORKTREES_DIR/$WORKTREE_NAME\" -b \"feat/$TASK_ID\" origin/main 2>/dev/null || {\n    echo \"Worktree exists, cleaning...\"\n    git worktree remove \"$WORKTREES_DIR/$WORKTREE_NAME\" 2>/dev/null || true\n    git worktree add \"$WORKTREES_DIR/$WORKTREE_NAME\" -b \"feat/$TASK_ID\" origin/main\n}\n\ncd \"$WORKTREES_DIR/$WORKTREE_NAME\"\n\n# 安装依赖\necho \"📦 Installing dependencies...\"\npnpm install --silent 2>/dev/null || npm install --silent 2>/dev/null || true\n\n# 启动 tmux 会话\nTMUX_SESSION=\"$AGENT_TYPE-$TASK_ID\"\nLOG_FILE=\"$LOGS_DIR/$TASK_ID.log\"\necho \"🤖 Starting agent in tmux: $TMUX_SESSION\"\n\ntmux new-session -d -s \"$TMUX_SESSION\" \\\n    -c \"$WORKTREES_DIR/$WORKTREE_NAME\"\n\n# 发送指令到会话\ntmux send-keys -t \"$TMUX_SESSION\" \"echo '=== Task: $TASK_ID ==='\" Enter\ntmux send-keys -t \"$TMUX_SESSION\" \"echo 'Started at: \\$(date)'\" Enter\ntmux send-keys -t \"$TMUX_SESSION\" \"echo 'Prompt: $PROMPT'\" Enter\ntmux send-keys -t \"$TMUX_SESSION\" \"\" Enter\ntmux send-keys -t \"$TMUX_SESSION\" \"# Running Claude Code...\" Enter\ntmux send-keys -t \"$TMUX_SESSION\" \"$CLAUDE_CODE_PATH --prompt \\\"$PROMPT\\\" --model $CLAUDE_MODEL 2>&1 | tee $LOG_FILE\" Enter\n\n# 记录任务\ncat > \"$TASKS_DIR/$TASK_ID.json\" << EOF\n{\n  \"id\": \"$TASK_ID\",\n  \"tmuxSession\": \"$TMUX_SESSION\",\n  \"agent\": \"$AGENT_TYPE\",\n  \"worktree\": \"$WORKTREE_NAME\",\n  \"branch\": \"feat/$TASK_ID\",\n  \"startedAt\": $(date +%s),\n  \"status\": \"running\",\n  \"prompt\": \"$PROMPT\",\n  \"retryCount\": 0\n}\nEOF\n\necho \"✅ Agent $TASK_ID started in tmux session $TMUX_SESSION\"\necho \"   Attach with: tmux attach -t $TMUX_SESSION\"\necho \"   Logs: $LOG_FILE\"\nSCRIPT\n```\n\n### 步骤 4: 创建监控脚本\n\n```bash\ncat > ~/openclaw-agents/scripts/monitor/loop.sh << 'SCRIPT'\n#!/bin/bash\n# 改进版 Ralph Loop - 监控所有 Agent 任务\n\nAGENTS_ROOT=~/openclaw-agents\nTASKS_DIR=$AGENTS_ROOT/tasks\nLOGS_DIR=$AGENTS_ROOT/logs\nCONFIG_FILE=$AGENTS_ROOT/config.json\n\n# 读取邮件配置\nEMAIL_ENABLED=$(jq -r '.email.enabled' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"false\")\nSMTP_SERVER=$(jq -r '.email.smtpServer' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"smtp.qq.com\")\nSMTP_PORT=$(jq -r '.email.smtpPort' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"587\")\nEMAIL_USER=$(jq -r '.email.username' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"\")\nEMAIL_PASS=$(jq -r '.email.password' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"\")\nEMAIL_FROM=$(jq -r '.email.from' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"\")\nEMAIL_TO=$(jq -r '.email.to' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"\")\n\n# 发送邮件函数\nsend_email() {\n    local subject=\"$1\"\n    local body=\"$2\"\n    \n    if [ \"$EMAIL_ENABLED\" != \"true\" ] || [ -z \"$EMAIL_USER\" ]; then\n        echo \"[EMAIL SKIP] $subject\"\n        return\n    fi\n    \n    python3 << PYEOF\nimport smtplib\nfrom email.mime.text import MIMEText\n\nmsg = MIMEText('''$body''')\nmsg['Subject'] = '$subject'\nmsg['From'] = '$EMAIL_FROM'\nmsg['To'] = '$EMAIL_TO'\n\ntry:\n    server = smtplib.SMTP('$SMTP_SERVER', $SMTP_PORT)\n    server.starttls()\n    server.login('$EMAIL_USER', '$EMAIL_PASS')\n    server.send_message(msg)\n    server.quit()\n    print(\"Email sent: $subject\")\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"Email failed: {e}\")\nPYEOF\n}\n\n# 主监控循环\nfor task_file in \"$TASKS_DIR\"/*.json; do\n    [ -f \"$task_file\" ] || continue\n    \n    TASK_ID=$(jq -r '.id' \"$task_file\" 2>/dev/null)\n    TMUX_SESSION=$(jq -r '.tmuxSession' \"$task_file\" 2>/dev/null)\n    STATUS=$(jq -r '.status' \"$task_file\" 2>/dev/null)\n    PROMPT=$(jq -r '.prompt' \"$task_file\" 2>/dev/null)\n    \n    [ -z \"$TASK_ID\" ] && continue\n    \n    echo \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] Checking task: $TASK_ID (status: $STATUS)\"\n    \n    # 检查 tmux 会话是否存活\n    if ! tmux has-session -t \"$TMUX_SESSION\" 2>/dev/null; then\n        echo \"[$TASK_ID] Session ended, checking results...\"\n        \n        LOG_FILE=\"$LOGS_DIR/$TASK_ID.log\"\n        \n        # 检查是否有 PR 创建\n        if [ -f \"$LOG_FILE\" ]; then\n            PR_LOG=$(grep -i \"Created PR\\|Pull request\\|github.com.*/pull\" \"$LOG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null | tail -1 || echo \"\")\n        else\n            PR_LOG=\"\"\n        fi\n        \n        if [ -n \"$PR_LOG\" ]; then\n            PR_URL=$(echo \"$PR_LOG\" | grep -oE 'https://github.com[^ >]+' | head -1)\n            \n            if [ -n \"$PR_URL\" ]; then\n                send_email \"🎉 PR Ready: $TASK_ID\" \"PR #$TASK_ID is ready for review.\\n\\nURL: $PR_URL\\nTask: $PROMPT\"\n                jq '.status = \"ready_review\" | .completedAt = '\"$(date +%s)\"'' \"$task_file\" > \"$task_file.tmp\"\n                mv \"$task_file.tmp\" \"$task_file\"\n            else\n                send_email \"⚠️ Task Completed: $TASK_ID\" \"Task #$TASK_ID completed but no PR created.\\n\\nPrompt: $PROMPT\\nCheck logs: $LOG_FILE\"\n                jq '.status = \"completed_no_pr\" | .completedAt = '\"$(date +%s)\"'' \"$task_file\" > \"$task_file.tmp\"\n                mv \"$task_file.tmp\" \"$task_file\"\n            fi\n        else\n            RETRY_COUNT=$(jq -r '.retryCount // 0' \"$task_file\")\n            MAX_RETRIES=3\n            \n            if [ \"$RETRY_COUNT\" -lt \"$MAX_RETRIES\" ]; then\n                echo \"[$TASK_ID] Retrying... ($RETRY_COUNT/$MAX_RETRIES)\"\n                send_email \"🔄 Retrying: $TASK_ID\" \"Task #$TASK_ID failed, retrying ($RETRY_COUNT/$MAX_RETRIES).\\n\\nPrompt: $PROMPT\"\n                jq '.retryCount = (.retryCount // 0) + 1 | .status = \"retrying\"' \"$task_file\" > \"$task_file.tmp\"\n                mv \"$task_file.tmp\" \"$task_file\"\n            else\n                send_email \"❌ Task Failed: $TASK_ID\" \"Task #$TASK_ID failed after $MAX_RETRIES retries.\\n\\nPrompt: $PROMPT\"\n                jq '.status = \"failed\" | .failedAt = '\"$(date +%s)\"'' \"$task_file\" > \"$task_file.tmp\"\n                mv \"$task_file.tmp\" \"$task_file\"\n            fi\n        fi\n    fi\ndone\n\necho \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] Monitor loop completed\"\nSCRIPT\n```\n\n### 步骤 5: 创建邮件通知脚本\n\n```bash\ncat > ~/openclaw-agents/scripts/notify/email.sh << 'SCRIPT'\n#!/bin/bash\n# 邮件通知脚本\n# 用法: ./email.sh <subject> <body>\n\nSUBJECT=$1\nBODY=$2\nCONFIG_FILE=~/openclaw-agents/config.json\n\nEMAIL_ENABLED=$(jq -r '.email.enabled' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"false\")\nSMTP_SERVER=$(jq -r '.email.smtpServer' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"smtp.qq.com\")\nSMTP_PORT=$(jq -r '.email.smtpPort' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"587\")\nEMAIL_USER=$(jq -r '.email.username' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"\")\nEMAIL_PASS=$(jq -r '.email.password' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"\")\nEMAIL_FROM=$(jq -r '.email.from' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"\")\nEMAIL_TO=$(jq -r '.email.to' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"\")\n\nif [ \"$EMAIL_ENABLED\" != \"true\" ] || [ -z \"$EMAIL_USER\" ]; then\n    echo \"Email not configured, skipping notification\"\n    exit 0\nfi\n\npython3 << PYEOF\nimport smtplib\nfrom email.mime.text import MIMEText\n\nmsg = MIMEText('''$BODY''')\nmsg['Subject'] = '$SUBJECT'\nmsg['From'] = '$EMAIL_FROM'\nmsg['To'] = '$EMAIL_TO'\n\ntry:\n    server = smtplib.SMTP('$SMTP_SERVER', $SMTP_PORT)\n    server.starttls()\n    server.login('$EMAIL_USER', '$EMAIL_PASS')\n    server.send_message(msg)\n    server.quit()\n    print(\"Email sent: $SUBJECT\")\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f\"Email failed: {e}\")\n    exit(1)\nPYEOF\nSCRIPT\n```\n\n### 步骤 6: 设置执行权限和 Cron\n\n```bash\n# 设置执行权限\nchmod +x ~/openclaw-agents/scripts/*.sh\nchmod +x ~/openclaw-agents/scripts/*/*.sh\n\n# 配置 Cron（每 10 分钟检查一次）\n(crontab -l 2>/dev/null | grep -v \"loop.sh\"; echo \"*/10 * * * * ~/openclaw-agents/scripts/monitor/loop.sh >> ~/openclaw-agents/logs/monitor.log 2>&1\") | crontab -\n\n# 验证 Cron\ncrontab -l\n```\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 验证清单\n\n```bash\n# 1. 检查目录结构\nls -la ~/openclaw-agents/\n\n# 2. 检查配置文件（记得修改 QQ 授权码）\ncat ~/openclaw-agents/config.json\n\n# 3. 测试 Agent 启动\ncd ~/openclaw-agents/scripts\n./start-agent.sh test-task default \"Hello World\" test-worktree\n\n# 4. 检查 tmux\ntmux list-sessions\n\n# 5. 检查任务记录\ncat ~/openclaw-agents/tasks/test-task.json\n\n# 6. 测试监控\n~/openclaw-agents/scripts/monitor/loop.sh\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📝 待完成事项\n\n1. **获取 QQ 邮箱授权码**\n   - 登录 https://mail.qq.com\n   - 设置 → 账户 → POP3/IMAP/SMTP/Exchange/CardDAV/CalDAV 服务\n   - 开启 IMAP/SMTP 服务\n   - 生成授权码\n   - 替换 `~/openclaw-agents/config.json` 中的 `YOUR_QQ_AUTH_CODE`\n\n2. **确认 Claude Code 路径**\n   - 检查 `~/.codex-agent/run-agent.sh` 是否存在\n   - 如不存在，修改 config.json 中的 `claudeCode.path`\n\n3. **确认 GitHub 仓库**\n   - 在 `/Users/lihzz/openclawCode` 中运行 `git remote -v`\n   - 确认 remote URL 正确\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 完成后告诉我\n\n执行完以上命令并配置好 QQ 授权码后，告诉我，我会帮你：\n1. 验证配置\n2. 测试 Agent 启动\n3. 测试邮件通知\n\n🦞\nuser: Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-03 15:51 GMT+8] 帮我看看我现在文件夹下的文件有哪些\nassistant: 我当前没有文件读写权限