{"type":"message","id":"6d3da746","parentId":"ededbdd0","timestamp":"2026-03-03T18:13:48.161Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户运行了 ./start.sh daily，系统成功运行但有几个问题需要修复：\n\n1. 搜索 API 未配置 - 研究员使用了示例数据而不是 Tavily API\n2. GitHub 仓库创建失败 - Token 权限不足（403 错误）\n3. 邮件通知未发送 - 需要添加邮件发送功能\n\n我需要：\n1. 修复研究员使用 Tavily API\n2. 修复 GitHub 权限问题（可能需要用户手动创建仓库或调整权限）\n3. 添加邮件发送简报功能\n\n让我先查看研究员代码，然后修复这些问题。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n看到运行结果了！有几个问题需要修复：\n\n1. ⚠️ **搜索 API 未使用** - 研究员还在用示例数据，没调用 Tavily\n2. ❌ **GitHub 仓库创建失败** - Token 权限不足（403 错误）\n3. ⚠️ **邮件未发送** - 需要添加邮件发送功能\n\n让我逐个修复：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2b632371abb74981afe2c7e4","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/lihzz/openclawCompany/agents/researcher.py","limit":100}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"local-qwen2","model":"Qwen3.5-122B-A10B-FP8","usage":{"input":62460,"output":262,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62722,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772561620263}}
{"type":"message","id":"c97ee0b6","parentId":"6d3da746","timestamp":"2026-03-03T18:13:48.184Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_2b632371abb74981afe2c7e4","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nResearcher - 资深 AI 技术前沿调研研究员\n自动爬取微信公众号和新闻，跟踪三大运营商、互联网热点、AI 大模型与智能体方向\n\"\"\"\nimport json\nimport time\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import List, Dict\nimport sys\nfrom pathlib import Path\nsys.path.insert(0, str(Path(__file__).parent.parent))\n\nfrom config import (\n    COMPANY_DIR, SHARED_MEMORY, HOTSPOT_KEYWORDS, COMPETITORS,\n    AI_TECH_ACCOUNTS, OPERATOR_ACCOUNTS, INTERNET_ACCOUNTS, MARKET_ACCOUNTS,\n    ALL_ACCOUNTS, CRAWL_STRATEGY\n)\n\n\nclass SeniorAIResearcher:\n    \"\"\"资深 AI 技术前沿调研研究员\"\"\"\n    \n    def __init__(self):\n        self.log_file = COMPANY_DIR / \"logs\" / \"researcher.log\"\n        self.output_dir = COMPANY_DIR / \"output\" / \"research\"\n        self.output_dir.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n        \n        self.hotspots = []\n        self.start_time = time.time()\n    \n    def log(self, message: str):\n        \"\"\"记录日志\"\"\"\n        timestamp = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\")\n        log_entry = f\"[{timestamp}] [SENIOR_RESEARCHER] {message}\\n\"\n        print(log_entry.strip())\n        with open(self.log_file, \"a\") as f:\n            f.write(log_entry)\n    \n    def search_with_tavily(self, query: str, category: str = \"general\") -> List[Dict]:\n        \"\"\"\n        使用 Tavily Search 搜索信息\n        如果没有 Tavily，使用 Brave Search 作为替代\n        \"\"\"\n        try:\n            import requests\n            import os\n            \n            # 尝试使用 Tavily API\n            tavily_api_key = os.getenv(\"TAVILY_API_KEY\", \"\")\n            \n            if tavily_api_key:\n                response = requests.post(\n                    \"https://api.tavily.com/search\",\n                    json={\n                        \"api_key\": tavily_api_key,\n                        \"query\": query,\n                        \"search_depth\": \"advanced\",\n                        \"include_domains\": [\"weixin.qq.com\", \"36kr.com\", \"qbitai.com\"],\n                        \"max_results\": 5\n                    },\n                    timeout=10\n                )\n                \n                if response.status_code == 200:\n                    results = response.json().get(\"results\", [])\n                    return [\n                        {\n                            \"title\": r.get(\"title\", \"\"),\n                            \"url\": r.get(\"url\", \"\"),\n                            \"content\": r.get(\"content\", \"\")[:500],\n                            \"source\": \"Tavily\",\n                            \"category\": category\n                        }\n                        for r in results\n                    ]\n            \n            # 备用：使用 Brave Search\n            brave_api_key = os.getenv(\"BRAVE_API_KEY\", \"\")\n            if brave_api_key:\n                headers = {\"X-Subscription-Token\": brave_api_key}\n                response = requests.get(\n                    \"https://api.search.brave.com/res/v1/web/search\",\n                    params={\"q\": query, \"count\": 5},\n                    headers=headers,\n                    timeout=10\n                )\n                \n                if response.status_code == 200:\n                    results = response.json().get(\"web\", {}).get(\"results\", [])\n                    return [\n                        {\n                            \"title\": r.get(\"title\", \"\"),\n                            \"url\": r.get(\"url\", \"\"),\n                            \"content\": r.get(\"snippet\", \"\")[:500],\n                            \"source\": \"Brave\",\n                            \"category\": category\n                        }\n                        for r in results\n\n[273 more lines in file. Use offset=101 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772561628177}}
