{"type":"message","id":"4934407d","parentId":"c6ad834f","timestamp":"2026-03-03T18:14:26.501Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_c72424aeecbc473f940fc9ac","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n---\n\n## 🔥 本周热点 Top 3\n\"\"\"\n        for i, event in enumerate(top_3, 1):\n            report += f\"\"\"\n### {i}. {event.get('heat_tag', '⚡')} **{event.get('title', '')[:50]}** \n- **主体**: {event.get('subject', '未知')}\n- **进展**: {event.get('summary', '')[:100]}\n- **影响**: {event.get('impact', {}).get('level', '中')} → {event.get('impact', {}).get('reason', '')}\n- **标签**: {' | '.join(event.get('category_tags', []))}\n- **来源**: {', '.join(event.get('sources', [event.get('source', '未知')]))}\n\"\"\"\n        \n        # 分类列表\n        report += \"\"\"\n---\n\n## 📡 分类详情\n\"\"\"\n        for category, items in categorized.items():\n            if items:\n                report += f\"\\n### {category} ({len(items)}条)\\n\"\n                for item in items[:5]:\n                    report += f\"- {item.get('heat_tag', '⚡')} **{item.get('title', '')[:40]}** - {item.get('subject', '')}\\n\"\n        \n        # 运营商动态表格\n        if operators:\n            report += \"\"\"\n---\n\n## 📡 运营商动态\n\n| 公司 | 事件 | 类型 | 链接 |\n|------|------|------|------|\n\"\"\"\n            for op in operators[:5]:\n                report += f\"| {op.get('subject', '')} | {op.get('title', '')[:20]}... | {op.get('event_type', '')} | [查看]({op.get('url', '#')}) |\\n\"\n        \n        # 市场洞察\n        market_events = [e for e in events if any(kw in e.get(\"title\", \"\") for kw in [\"IDC\", \"艾瑞\", \"市场\", \"报告\", \"融资\"])]\n        if market_events:\n            report += \"\"\"\n---\n\n## 📈 市场洞察\n\"\"\"\n            for event in market_events[:3]:\n                report += f\"- {event.get('title', '')}\\n\"\n        \n        # 下周关注\n        report += \"\"\"\n---\n\n## 📅 下周关注\n- 华为开发者大会：盘古大模型新版本是否发布？\n- 智谱 AI 将开源 AutoGLM 工具链\n- 各大模型厂商 Q1 业绩报告\n\n---\n\n**📊 报告生成时间**: {time} | **🤖 by AI Content Editor** | **📈 共 {total} 条情报**\n\n*本报告由 AI 技术前沿调研系统自动生成*\n\"\"\".format(\n            time=datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M\"),\n            total=len(events)\n        )\n        \n        return report\n    \n    def _get_report_link(self, date: str) -> str:\n        \"\"\"获取报告链接\"\"\"\n        if self.github_pages_config[\"enabled\"]:\n            return f\"https://{self.github_pages_config['username']}.github.io/{self.github_pages_config['repo']}/{date}.html\"\n        return \"https://example.com/report\"  # 占位符\n    \n    def save_report(self, report: str, date: str) -> Path:\n        \"\"\"保存报告\"\"\"\n\n[195 more lines in file. Use offset=380 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772561666489}}
