{"type":"message","id":"3bb1b1b3","parentId":"9d1745e4","timestamp":"2026-03-03T18:47:49.074Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_fa1e28ada17a49de9e693a53","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\r\n  \"message\": \"Bad credentials\",\r\n  \"documentation_url\": \"https://docs.github.com/rest\",\r\n  \"status\": \"401\"\r\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":637,"aggregated":"{\r\n  \"message\": \"Bad credentials\",\r\n  \"documentation_url\": \"https://docs.github.com/rest\",\r\n  \"status\": \"401\"\r\n}","cwd":"/Users/lihzz/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772563669056}}
{"type":"message","id":"c02381e7","parentId":"3bb1b1b3","timestamp":"2026-03-03T18:48:08.978Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Token 确实过期了，现在需要创建一个智能体架构方案文档，解决用户指出的核心问题：系统无法自动纠正错误。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nToken 确实过期了。现在让我给你一个**真正的智能体架构升级方案**，解决你指出的核心问题：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_530508d04c6540e19984267b","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 🤖 AI 公司 - 智能体架构升级方案\n\n## 🎯 当前问题\n\n### ❌ 硬编码流程的问题\n\n```python\n# 当前架构：硬编码\nresult = subprocess.run([\"git\", \"push\", \"-u\", \"origin\", \"main\"])\nif result.returncode != 0:\n    print(\"❌ 推送失败\")\n    # 结束，等待人工介入\n```\n\n**问题**:\n1. 遇到错误就停止，无法自动纠正\n2. 不知道有哪些纠正策略\n3. 无法从失败中学习\n4. 每次遇到同样错误都要人工处理\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 智能体架构设计\n\n### 核心理念\n\n**Agent 应该能够**:\n1. **检测错误** - 识别错误类型\n2. **尝试纠正** - 自动应用纠正策略\n3. **记录学习** - 积累经验\n4. **持续进化** - 下次遇到类似错误自动应用已验证的方案\n\n---\n\n## 🏗️ 架构升级\n\n### 1. 错误检测与分类层\n\n```python\nclass ErrorDetector:\n    \"\"\"错误检测器 - 识别错误类型并分类\"\"\"\n    \n    ERROR_PATTERNS = {\n        \"git_conflict\": [\n            \"Updates were rejected because the remote contains work\",\n            \"fetch first\",\n            \"non-fast-forward\"\n        ],\n        \"auth_failed\": [\n            \"Bad credentials\",\n            \"401 Unauthorized\",\n            \"permission denied\"\n        ],\n        \"rate_limit\": [\n            \"rate limit exceeded\",\n            \"403 Forbidden\"\n        ],\n        \"network\": [\n            \"connection refused\",\n            \"timeout\",\n            \"network unreachable\"\n        ]\n    }\n    \n    def detect(self, error_message: str) -> str:\n        \"\"\"识别错误类型\"\"\"\n        for error_type, patterns in self.ERROR_PATTERNS.items():\n            for pattern in patterns:\n                if pattern.lower() in error_message.lower():\n                    return error_type\n        return \"unknown\"\n```\n\n### 2. 纠正策略引擎\n\n```python\nclass CorrectionStrategy:\n    \"\"\"纠正策略引擎 - 根据错误类型选择纠正方案\"\"\"\n    \n    STRATEGIES = {\n        \"git_conflict\": [\n            {\"action\": \"git_pull_rebase\", \"description\": \"先 pull --rebase 同步\"},\n            {\"action\": \"git_push_force\", \"description\": \"强制推送覆盖\"},\n            {\"action\": \"git_reset_hard\", \"description\": \"重置本地仓库\"},\n        ],\n        \"auth_failed\": [\n            {\"action\": \"refresh_token\", \"description\": \"刷新 Token\"},\n            {\"action\": \"retry_with_new_token\", \"description\": \"使用备用 Token\"},\n        ],\n        \"rate_limit\": [\n            {\"action\": \"wait_and_retry\", \"description\": \"等待后重试\"},\n            {\"action\": \"exponential_backoff\", \"description\": \"指数退避\"},\n        ],\n        \"network\": [\n            {\"action\": \"retry\", \"description\": \"简单重试\"},\n            {\"action\": \"check_network\", \"description\": \"检查网络连接\"},\n        ]\n    }\n    \n    def get_strategies(self, error_type: str) -> list:\n        \"\"\"获取纠正策略列表\"\"\"\n        return self.STRATEGIES.get(error_type, [{\"action\": \"manual\", \"description\": \"人工介入\"}])\n```\n\n### 3. 学习记忆系统\n\n```python\nclass LearningMemory:\n    \"\"\"学习记忆 - 记录成功和失败的纠正经验\"\"\"\n    \n    def __init__(self, memory_file: Path):\n        self.memory_file = memory_file\n        self.memory = self._load_memory()\n    \n    def _load_memory(self) -> dict:\n        \"\"\"加载记忆\"\"\"\n        if self.memory_file.exists():\n            with open(self.memory_file, \"r\") as f:\n                return json.load(f)\n        return {\"successful_corrections\": [], \"failed_attempts\": []}\n    \n    def record_success(self, error_type: str, strategy: str, context: dict):\n        \"\"\"记录成功的纠正\"\"\"\n        self.memory[\"successful_corrections\"].append({\n            \"error_type\": error_type,\n            \"strategy\": strategy,\n            \"context\": context,\n            \"timestamp\": datetime.now().isoformat()\n        })\n        self._save_memory()\n    \n    def record_failure(self, error_type: str, strategy: str, error: str):\n        \"\"\"记录失败的纠正\"\"\"\n        self.memory[\"failed_attempts\"].append({\n            \"error_type\": error_type,\n            \"strategy\": strategy,\n            \"error\": error,\n            \"timestamp\": datetime.now().isoformat()\n        })\n        self._save_memory()\n    \n    def get_best_strategy(self, error_type: str) -> str:\n        \"\"\"根据历史经验获取最佳策略\"\"\"\n        # 统计哪种策略成功率最高\n        successes = [\n            c for c in self.memory[\"successful_corrections\"]\n            if c[\"error_type\"] == error_type\n        ]\n        \n        strategy_counts = {}\n        for s in successes:\n            strategy = s[\"strategy\"]\n            strategy_counts[strategy] = strategy_counts.get(strategy, 0) + 1\n        \n        if strategy_counts:\n            return max(strategy_counts, key=strategy_counts.get)\n        return None\n```\n\n### 4. 智能执行器\n\n```python\nclass SmartExecutor:\n    \"\"\"智能执行器 - 带错误纠正的执行引擎\"\"\"\n    \n    def __init__(self):\n        self.error_detector = ErrorDetector()\n        self.strategy_engine = CorrectionStrategy()\n        self.memory = LearningMemory(COMPANY_DIR / \"memory\" / \"corrections.json\")\n    \n    def execute_with_retry(self, command: list, max_retries: int = 3) -> tuple:\n        \"\"\"执行命令，失败时自动尝试纠正\"\"\"\n        for attempt in range(max_retries):\n            result = subprocess.run(command, capture_output=True, text=True)\n            \n            if result.returncode == 0:\n                return True, result\n            \n            # 检测错误\n            error_type = self.error_detector.detect(result.stderr)\n            \n            # 获取最佳策略\n            best_strategy = self.memory.get_best_strategy(error_type)\n            strategies = self.strategy_engine.get_strategies(error_type)\n            \n            # 如果有历史最佳策略，优先使用\n            if best_strategy:\n                strategies = [s for s in strategies if s[\"action\"] == best_strategy] + strategies\n            \n            # 尝试纠正策略\n            if attempt < len(strategies):\n                strategy = strategies[attempt]\n                print(f\"   ⚠️ 错误：{error_type}\")\n                print(f\"   🔧 应用纠正策略：{strategy['description']}\")\n                \n                if self._apply_strategy(strategy[\"action\"]):\n                    self.memory.record_success(error_type, strategy[\"action\"], {\"attempt\": attempt})\n                    # 重新执行命令\n                    continue\n            \n            # 所有策略都失败，记录并返回\n            self.memory.record_failure(error_type, strategies[-1][\"action\"] if strategies else \"unknown\", result.stderr)\n            return False, result\n    \n    def _apply_strategy(self, strategy: str) -> bool:\n        \"\"\"应用纠正策略\"\"\"\n        strategies = {\n            \"git_pull_rebase\": lambda: subprocess.run([\"git\", \"pull\", \"--rebase\"], check=False).returncode == 0,\n            \"git_push_force\": lambda: subprocess.run([\"git\", \"push\", \"--force\"], check=False).returncode == 0,\n            \"retry\": lambda: True,  # 简单重试\n            \"wait_and_retry\": lambda: (time.sleep(5), True)[1],\n            \"manual\": lambda: False,\n        }\n        return strategies.get(strategy, lambda: False)()\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📁 文件结构\n\n```\nopenclawCompany/\n├── agents/\n│   ├── core/\n│   │   ├── error_detector.py    # 错误检测\n│   │   ├── strategy_engine.py   # 策略引擎\n│   │   ├── learning_memory.py   # 学习记忆\n│   │   └── smart_executor.py    # 智能执行\n│   ├── researcher.py\n│   ├── analyst.py\n│   ├── developer.py\n│   ├── content.py\n│   └── monitor.py\n├── memory/\n│   ├── corrections.json         # 纠正经验记忆\n│   ├── today_research_summary.md\n│   └── ...\n└── scripts/\n    └── test_github_full.py      # 已升级的测试脚本\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 立即实施计划\n\n### 阶段 1: 修复测试脚本（已完成）\n- ✅ 添加错误检测和纠正策略\n- ✅ 添加 pull --rebase + push --force 双策略\n- ✅ 改进清理逻辑\n\n### 阶段 2: 核心架构（待实施）\n- [ ] 创建 `agents/core/` 目录\n- [ ] 实现 `ErrorDetector` 类\n- [ ] 实现 `CorrectionStrategy` 类\n- [ ] 实现 `LearningMemory` 类\n- [ ] 实现 `SmartExecutor` 类\n\n### 阶段 3: 集成到现有 Agent（待实施）\n- [ ] 修改 `developer.py` 使用 `SmartExecutor`\n- [ ] 修改 `researcher.py` 使用 `SmartExecutor`\n- [ ] 所有 subprocess 调用替换为智能执行\n\n### 阶段 4: 学习系统（待实施）\n- [ ] 记录每次成功/失败的纠正\n- [ ] 自动统计最佳策略\n- [ ] 定期生成学习报告\n\n---\n\n## 💡 预期效果\n\n### 当前（硬编码）\n```\n遇到 git 推送冲突 → 失败 → 等待人工处理\n```\n\n### 升级后（智能体）\n```\n遇到 git 推送冲突 \n  → 检测错误类型：git_conflict\n  → 尝试策略 1: pull --rebase\n  → 如果失败，尝试策略 2: push --force\n  → 如果成功，记录经验\n  → 下次遇到同样错误，优先使用已验证的策略\n  → 自动完成，无需人工介入\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📊 学习记忆示例\n\n```json\n{\n  \"successful_corrections\": [\n    {\n      \"error_type\": \"git_conflict\",\n      \"strategy\": \"git_push_force\",\n      \"context\": {\"repo\": \"test-ai-project\", \"attempt\": 1},\n      \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-04T02:45:00\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"error_type\": \"auth_failed\", \n      \"strategy\": \"refresh_token\",\n      \"context\": {\"service\": \"github\"},\n      \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-04T01:30:00\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"failed_attempts\": [\n    {\n      \"error_type\": \"git_conflict\",\n      \"strategy\": \"git_pull_rebase\",\n      \"error\": \"conflict cannot be resolved automatically\",\n      \"timestamp\": \"2026-03-04T02:44:55\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 下一步行动\n\n1. **修复 Token** - 生成新的 GitHub Token\n2. **测试修复后的脚本** - 验证错误纠正逻辑\n3. **实施核心架构** - 创建 `agents/core/` 目录和类\n4. **集成到开发者 Agent** - 让 `developer.py` 使用智能执行器\n\n---\n\n**这是从\"硬编码流程\"到\"真正智能体\"的关键升级！** 🚀\n","path":"/Users/lihzz/openclawCompany/AGENT_ARCHITECTURE_UPGRADE.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"local-qwen2","model":"Qwen3.5-122B-A10B-FP8","usage":{"input":106512,"output":2709,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109221,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772563669075}}
